race.comment: ANGEL IN BLACK (1) clearly has talent and she tackled a tougher race at her last run back in November when sixth behind Motorsports in the G3 Blue Sapphire Stakes. Narrowly beaten in maiden grade the start prior, so can start with a bang here. GOLD COAST BELLE (5) made a promising debut over 1000m at this track on September 11, finishing 0.8 lengths off a handy one. Placed in a recent trial. Sure to have improved so expected to run well again. MILOS FILOS (9) draws the pole and made an encouraging return last start in a handy race, so she looks to have come back well. SAPPHIRE REIGN (10) has not raced since her debut back on September 7 when she finished fifth over 1100m at Bendigo. Might not have loved the Heavy 9 that day and has trialled well since.
